snow-raking
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the making of tracks in snow to enable trapped stock to walk out to levels below a snow line.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes:
